Version: 3 (BUILD 3.89)
Version Notes: 

-Added new "AUTO PING" feature! - will activate upon aiming and shooting, and will ping enemies automatically for you.
-Re-tweaked aim assists.
-Improved dynamic aim assist, which increases your aim assist strength upon aiming + shooting.
-Fixed Anti-Recoil issues.
-Testing Rapid Fire for future implemenation.

